  sgcool_label_text: This commemorative issue was published by the Straits Times to celebrate Singapore’s 6th National Day. It contains write-ups on Singapore\u0027s history
 a discussion of the economic problems it faces
 Singapore\u0027s rapid development
 and articles relating to the country\u0027s infant air defence force.
